<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>{{ title }} — Guide Photographe</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script>(function(){var t=localStorage.getItem('theme')||'dark';document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme',t);})();</script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ '/assets/style.css' | url }}">
</head>
<body>

<button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="Menu" onclick="toggleNav()">☰</button>
<div class="nav-overlay" id="navOverlay" onclick="closeNav()"></div>

<header>
  <div class="header-label">Photographie · Art & Technique</div>
  <h1>Guide du <span>Photographe</span></h1>
  <p>De la prise de vue au rendu final — technique, regard et direction artistique pour photographes exigeants.</p>
  <div class="version-badge">Prise de vue · Traitement · Rendu</div>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <nav>
    {% include "nav.njk" %}
  </nav>

  <main>
    <div class="module">
      {{ content | safe }}
    </div>
  </main>
</div>

<div id="lexiqueTooltip" class="lexique-tooltip">
  <div class="ltt-name"></div>
  <div class="ltt-short"></div>
  <a class="ltt-link" href="">Voir dans le lexique →</a>
</div>

<button class="back-to-top" id="backToTop" aria-label="Retour en haut">↑</button>
<button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" aria-label="Basculer le thème" onclick="toggleTheme()">◑</button>

<script src="{{ '/assets/app.js' | url }}"></script>
</body>
</html>
